CAPTCHA-image with arbitrary size. The image was generated on the server, leading to excessive load for large-sized images. The issue was reintroduced (fixed in #204208) due to a patch that broke the good configuration. \n\n##Fix\n\nThe dimensions of the CAPTCHA was limited server side.\n\n##Reasoning\n\nThe flaw was very simple and even simpler to exploit, but the potential business impact was significant. Very much a stealthy DOS potentially hard to pinpoint. The bounty reflects the potential business impact.\n","can_view?":true,"can_edit?":false,"content_html":"\u003ch2 id=\"issue\"\u003eIssue\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe reporter was able to craft an http-request to request a CAPTCHA-image with arbitrary size. The image was generated on the server, leading to excessive load for large-sized images. The issue was reintroduced (fixed in \u003ca href=\"/reports/204208\"\u003e#204208\u003c/a\u003e) due to a patch that broke the good configuration. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"fix\"\u003eFix\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe dimensions of the CAPTCHA was limited server side.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"reasoning\"\u003eReasoning\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe flaw was very simple and even simpler to exploit, but the potential business impact was significant. Very much a stealthy DOS potentially hard to pinpoint. The bounty reflects the potential business impact.\u003c/p\u003e\n"},{"id":6187,"category":"researcher","content":"Went through old disclosed bugs and found one that had reappeared due to changes in the codebase.","can_view?":true,"can_edit?":false,"content_html":"\u003cp\u003eWent through old disclosed bugs and found one that had reappeared due to changes in the codebase.\u003c/p\u003e\n"}]}